{"tid":535102,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求學英文方法","createTime":"2018-01-20T13:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T14:44:35.000Z","uid":166807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54e9071da1cab4e00a02b9546e74ce3d6f934757","tid":535102,"uid":166807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"本身英文好差<br />\n出嚟做咗野幾年<br />\n膽粗粗報左part time degree 讀返書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係發現自己啲英文個底真係太爛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家逼緊自己瘋狂睇textbook 瘋狂查字典補返靚個底佢<br />\n但發現好多字查完抄低都記唔曬<br />\n請問各位連登仔有無方法記下字同埋提升下睇英文書個速度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逐隻逐隻字查 oxford dictionary 真係睇得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e7163dadefbd92174452e4cb41478904a7f97d","tid":535102,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c162bbcb4799e2707de64aab8e8c8d698a4b8d5","tid":535102,"uid":166807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投過胎</blockquote><br />\n讚吓我無錯別字先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d32e10fbaf9b1b8f5aa2a189ccd90f8c128403","tid":535102,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:36:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc83f5d0a7cb256e126524cdcc032da9fdc791cd","tid":535102,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"reading 睇 time magazine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlistening 睇節目，一定要有英文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好聽歌學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d4c9ca20c7aadddb641b22130098735bb34917","tid":535102,"uid":166807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>reading 睇 time magazine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlistening 睇節目，一定要有英文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好聽歌學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係如果睇到每一句都有字要查字典但係自己又記唔住有咩好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前都有睇開美劇 不過依家無了<br />\n最無用嘅聽英文歌反而係我日常習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5941aec170afffa839e1e498fdcb525910beae","tid":535102,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7d4c9ca20c7aadddb641b22130098735bb34917","tid":535102,"uid":166807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>reading 睇 time magazine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlistening 睇節目，一定要有英文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好聽歌學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係如果睇到每一句都有字要查字典但係自己又記唔住有咩好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前都有睇開美劇 不過依家無了<br />\n最無用嘅聽英文歌反而係我日常習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"記生字係必經嘅階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你齋聽就冇所謂，但係攞來學英文就真係唔好嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb3acbcc20e3c39675ae7a322a09355bd50ce49","tid":535102,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"講多啲 要活學活用<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾starbucks subway呢啲地方局限自己<br />\n盡可能將生活中最習以為常嘅事以英文去同人溝通<br />\n<br />\n下次去譚仔澳牛用英文落單<br />\n喺街有人問路用英文答<br />\n睇港產片集中讀英文字幕"},{"pid":"381bba2d3db656a5e3a7332c795b55893be5d06c","tid":535102,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:12:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"04e53bbead3e2992ea9e3bcab4094e7c97f1f27e","tid":535102,"uid":82500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"認真睇戲<br />\n同埋要揀自己鍾意既<br />\n以前中學播埋啲濕鳩迪士尼，仲要無字幕，次次訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後自己上網睇啲<br />\nhang over, ted 嗰啲，有埋中英字幕<br />\n學得快好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49971a4f9b8601a6aa3100021c21bc4ea718e24","tid":535102,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"每日睇明珠新聞，聽下英文電台，搵d簡單d既野黎睇下先啦，無可能一黎就睇d好深既字"},{"pid":"07574ccb0126eee63099e6b08e7d87828a62f492","tid":535102,"uid":19087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7d4c9ca20c7aadddb641b22130098735bb34917","tid":535102,"uid":166807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>reading 睇 time magazine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlistening 睇節目，一定要有英文字幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好聽歌學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係如果睇到每一句都有字要查字典但係自己又記唔住有咩好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前都有睇開美劇 不過依家無了<br />\n最無用嘅聽英文歌反而係我日常習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得聽英文歌可以當係個 Introduction 咁，等你對英文有個感覺無咁排斥<br />\n當然你話學發音、文法個啲就唔好啦<br />\n久唔久都會有啲特別字/ 詞組出現<br />\n因為當你鐘意個首歌，你就會想搵歌詞跟住唱<br />\n遇到唔識嘅字就會去查點讀點發音 （再重申唔好用聽歌黎學發音、文法）<br />\n喺呢個過程會識到好多唔同嘅生字，同埋會有印象 <br />\n所以我覺得聽得多越好，最好聽多啲唔同類型嘅仲好<br />\n<br />\n其次就煲劇<br />\n依家啲字幕組好多都做曬中英雙字，有時仲會有註釋等你理解下啲角色引用黎做比喻嘅事<br />\n睇多左聽多左，會慢慢聽到佢地講嘅英文而唔洗喪追字幕<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得由呢2 方面入手會增加學英文嘅興趣<br />\n講真你日日睇 Text Book 真係會悶到令你越黎越唔想學"}]}